# Optional corporate root CA bundle. Empty in the upstream repo.
#
# Hosts behind a TLS-inspecting proxy (e.g. a SASE / firewall MITM) must
# populate this file with the proxy's root CA in PEM format before
# building images, otherwise `npm ci` and `go mod download` will fail
# with "certificate verify failed". Use:
#
#   scripts/inject-host-ca.sh
#
# to copy the host's trusted CA bundle here. Do not commit a populated
# version of this file.
